<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title><para>A <tag>step</tag> identifies a unit of action in a
      <tag>procedure</tag>. If a finer level of granularity is
      required for some steps, you can embed <tag>substeps</tag> in a
      <tag>step</tag>. Embedded <tag>substeps</tag> contain
      <tag>step</tag>s so that substeps can be nested to any
      depth.</para>

      <refsection><info><title>Processing expectations</title></info>
        

        <para>Formatted as a displayed block. The <tag>step</tag>s are
        almost always numbered.</para>
</refsection>

